title: General view - [Manhattan - Lexington Avenue - 51st Street (East).]

text:
Lexington Ave., west side, south from East 52nd to 51st Streets, showing a new commercial and theatre structure under construction at the S.W. corner of the first point. Upon this site originally stood a Swedish M.E. Church, the sale of which was culminated in January 1937.
October 12, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
